text: The 2014 United States Soccer Federation presidential election was held in Chicago on March 1, 2014 to determine the next President of the United States Soccer Federation. Sunil Gulati ran unopposed and entered his third four-year term after having served as U.S. Soccer’s President since 2006. ==References== Category:Presidents of the United States Soccer Federation Category:2014 in American soccer
title: 2014 United States Soccer Federation presidential election
